{"tid":2289711,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[ibond] 行山銀行真係垃圾中嘅垃圾","createTime":"2020-11-17T12:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T13:42:34.000Z","uid":61161,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c933f78735aa4206890778bdfe8201425a0a1c9","tid":2289711,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"好似返咗九十年代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先你認購ibond個編號係K848, 要用證券戶口去持有呢個債券<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度都理解嘅<br />\n<br />\n如果你想用OTC場外交易沽出就要打電話(before 28/11)/去任何一間分行做報價同沽出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去任何一間分行填表格將個Bond code轉做Stock code (P.S. 過咗27/11要去指定分行)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分行已經忙到癲咗，數又跑唔到，啲客打上hotline, 閒閒地等成2-3個鐘先至輪到打得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係乜都要人手做，填form或者打電話，落後到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地匯豐都可以網上做OTC場外交易落盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nibond出咗幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到2020年仲玩鳩啲客同職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bffd47e4b91618984a6d21dbedaf017bca721a6","tid":2289711,"uid":75879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"好on9 佢竟然miss 我份application <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c604a81a4b456b3c57b22f53b2d76264b7ac111f","tid":2289711,"uid":217729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c933f78735aa4206890778bdfe8201425a0a1c9","tid":2289711,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"好似返咗九十年代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla